name: Katy o'Brian
description:
Katy M o'Brian. She's been in The Mandolorian, Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania, The Rookie and some other stuff.

I just thought she would make a great character for Cyberpunk themed images.

Trained on 29 image, 16 vector per token, used BLIP for captions (without checking results/lazy), 11,750 steps.

Don't know if it makes a difference but it was set to v1-5 when training but I use cyberrealistic_v13 for generation.

If you know better settings I should be using, please let me know.
